%^BOLD%^-=%^RED%^Tyranny Domain%^BOLD%^%^WHITE%^=-%^RESET%^

Clerics who choose the tyranny domain are typically fond of throwing their weight around and making others obey their  whims. The domain grants access to spells that affect the will of their foes as well as the ability of the foes to use certain magical abilities.

Clerics with the Tyranny Domain gain a +1 to caster level for enchantment sphere spells.

The tyranny domain contains the following spells:

Cause Fear, Oppression, Wave of Pain, Modify Memory, Fear, Forbiddance, Insanity, Orb Of The Void, Wail of The Banshee
%^CYAN%^Deities%^RESET%^: Lord Shadow

%^BOLD%^Please see individual help files for an explanation of what each spell does.%^RESET%^
